subject: Football (College)
Coaches and Managers
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Rutgers fired its defensive coordinator, Dave Cohen; its quarterbacks coach, Rob Spence; and its offensive line coach, Damian Wroblewski.
